JORKLE DICE (05/04/2026)

Players fill 7 cups of whatever drink they'd like. Players fill the solo cups to the second line.
All cups are randomly placed in the center of the table.
Players throw a ping pong ball counter clockwise catching and throwing with their dominant hand.

Goal: Have the highest cup tower at the end of the game!
    *Players attempt to drink as many cups as possible while still obeying the rules of the game.
     Players continue until no cups remain.

If a Player:

    Drops the ball,
    Makes a bad throw,
    Uses their non-dominant hand to catch/throw
    => -1 Cup *Players must remove their cup before drinking a new one.

Players can yell out the following to affect the game:

    Slort => Change Ball Direction
    Turkmenistan => Slap the ball before catching it (May hit the ground).

    *If two players say one of these at the same time -1 cup.

All players have a playing card face down in front of them. If one player flips their card, all other 
players must flip theirs as well. Last person to flip their card => -5 cups.

Players play two rounds & keep their tower from the previous round. Player with the highes tower wins:

First Round:

    1rst Place => 2pts
    2nd Place => 1pt

Second Round:

    1rst Place => 3pts + 1 ZORK
    2nd Place => 2pts
    Last Place => 1 shot!